AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Elevation
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT Elevation FROM Location WHERE Turbine = '%Element%' ORDER BY Elevation

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Installation Date
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [Installation Date] FROM Location WHERE Turbine = '%Element%' ORDER BY Installation Date

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Latitude
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT Latitude FROM Location WHERE Turbine = '%Element%' ORDER BY Latitude

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Longitude
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT Longitude FROM Location WHERE Turbine = '%Element%' ORDER BY Longitude

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Manufacturer
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT Manufacturer FROM Location WHERE Turbine = '%Element%' ORDER BY Manufacturer

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Model
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT Model FROM Location WHERE Turbine = '%Element%' ORDER BY Model

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Potential Power
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [Potential Power] FROM PowerCurve WHERE INTERPOLATE([Wind Speed], @[Adjusted Wind Speed;UOM=m/s])

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: A := Rand(1,0.08); Variable1 := If A>1 Then A-2 Else A;
TurbAWS := '..|Wind Speed'*Rand(1,0.2); Variable1 := If '..|Wind Speed'<20 And TurbAWS>=20 Then 19.99-Rand(0.1,0.1) Else If '..|Wind Speed'>=20 And TurbAWS<20 Then 20.01+Rand(0.1,0.1) Else TurbAWS;
